(520, 110, 'paragraphs_0_description', '<span lang=\"en\">The Ministry of Interior project owner, MOI has considered one of the best government agencies within the United Arab Emirates in terms of the quality of digital services it provides to all components of the UAE society, as it recently won several awards and is the best government entity in digital services, and the Ministry of Interior aspires to continuous improvement and to achieve strategic goals permanently. Accordingly, the Ministry of Interior launched the \"National Platform for Controlled Medication \", in collaboration and coordination with the stick holder all health authorities Ministry of Health and Prevention (MOHP), the </span><span lang=\"en-US\">Ministry of climate change and Environment (MOCCE), the Department of Health Abu Dhabi (DOH), Dubai Health Authority (DHA), Emirates Health Services (EHS), Federal Authority for identity citizenship, customs, port Security (ICA) and the private Health sector.</span>'),
