(524, 110, 'paragraphs_1_description', '<span lang=\"en-US\">The <b><i>National Platform for Controlled Medication:</i></b> created by <b><i>Tahaluf Al Emarat Technical Solution LLC</i></b>, </span>is a cutting-edge healthcare support portal whose mission is to pave the way for a healthier and secure future, by tracking the (POM) (narcotics, controlled and semi-controlled medication) from entering the country until they reach the patients’ hands, the health sector has witnessed great qualitative accomplishments in a bid to meet various health challenges in healthcare services and keep pace with global developments. We aim to advance and enhance the quality of healthcare services for the betterment of our society and all of UAE.<span lang=\"en\"> Establish an integrated tracking process for the movement of controlled drugs and restricted medicines. Also, for vet medication, and inventory tracking for all controlled medication, to reach to easy and safe use.</span>'),
